    section.slide
      h2 Robots Exclusion Protocol
      img(src='../../shared/resources/images/googlebot.png', class='corner-image', width='200px', alt='Googlebot')
      ul
        li First proposed in 1994 by Martijn Koster
        li De facto standard used by ~500,000,000 websites
        li Google officially 
          a(href="https://webmasters.googleblog.com/2019/07/rep-id.html") submitted it
          |  to the IETF with improvements
        li They also 
          a(href="https://github.com/google/robotstxt") open sourced
          |  Googlebot's robots.txt parser
      img(src="./images/robots-txt.jpg", alt="Robots.txt", style="max-width:40%")

    section.slide
