      img(src='./images/cloudflare-logo.png', class='corner-image', width='200px', alt='Cloudflare')
      ul
        li All Cloudflare-proxied domains went down on July 2
        li Cause: bad deployment of a <strong>single firewall regex rule</strong>
        li Resulted in 100% CPU spike across all proxy servers worldwide
        li Cloudflare's on-call support guy that day:
      img(src="./images/dawson.gif", alt="Dawson")

